main event: A witness saw a bright green object fall to the ground, resembling a meteor, in Parkersburg, West Virginia.
interesting points: The object lit up the sky and was thought to be about 1 mile away., The sighting lasted for about 10-15 seconds., The witness called the highway patrol about the incident., There were subsequent calls regarding the object, but details were illegible., The source of the report was a civilian.
sighted object: bright green object falling to the ground
